Package: TranscripTools
Title: Streamlined RNA-seq Data Manipulation and Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Francesco Edoardo Vallone", email = "francesco.edo.vallone@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: TranscripTools simplifies RNA-seq analysis with intuitive functions for differential gene expression, visualization, functional enrichment, and PCA. Designed for efficiency and reproducibility, it reduces complex workflows to a few lines of code.
